        <img src="https://api.metabolixmd.com/image/4.png" alt="MetabolixMD Logo" style="width: 50px; margin: 20px auto;">

        <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Thank you <b> <%= customerName %></b> for reaching out to <span style="color: #FA812F; font-weight: bold;">MetabolixMD</span>! We're excited to help you on your path to a healthier you. Our personalized weight loss programs are designed to provide the guidance, support, and medical expertise you need to reach your goals. With options including medications like <em>semaglutide</em> and <em>tirzepatide</em>, tailored nutrition plans, and regular consultations, we're here to help you succeed safely and effectively.</p>

        <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Our team will reach out soon to schedule your initial consultation. In the meantime, please feel free to email us for further queries at <span style="color: #2c665d; font-weight: bold;"><a href="mailto:consultant@metabolixmd.com">consultant@metabolixmd.com</a></span>.</p>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 20px 0;">

        <h2 style="color: #2c665d;">Here are a few tips to keep in mind while on medication</h2>

        <div style="text-align: left; margin-top: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Small, frequent meals</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Start with smaller portions spread throughout the day to ease nausea and digestion, common in the first month of tirzepatide use.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Focus on protein</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Prioritize lean proteins like chicken, fish, or tofu to maintain muscle mass and aid satiety while reducing overall calorie intake.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Choose fiber-rich foods</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Incorporate vegetables, fruits, and whole grains to promote digestion and reduce constipation, a possible side effect of GLP-1 drugs.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Stay hydrated</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Drink plenty of water (8-10 glasses a day) to help with digestion and manage potential side effects like nausea or bloating.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Avoid greasy or fatty foods</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">High-fat meals can increase nausea and stomach discomfort, so opt for lighter, low-fat options to reduce gastrointestinal issues.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Limit sugar intake</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Avoid sugary foods and beverages as they can spike blood sugar and counteract the appetite-controlling effects of tirzepatide.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Incorporate healthy fats</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Add small amounts of healthy fats like avocados, nuts, and olive oil to your meals to promote fullness without overwhelming digestion.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Monitor portion sizes</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Keep portions moderate to avoid overwhelming the stomach, which may already be slowed by tirzepatide, leading to discomfort.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Eat slowly and mindfully</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Chewing slowly and savoring meals can help prevent overeating and aid digestion, which is important while adjusting to GLP-1 medications.</p>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #2c665d; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Limit alcohol consumption</h3>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0; color: #333;">Alcohol can irritate the stomach and interfere with blood sugar regulation, so limit intake to avoid worsening side effects.</p>
        </div>

